ActivePermSetLicenseMetric.name: ActivePermSetLicenseMetric
ActivePermSetLicenseMetric.description: Represents the number of active, assigned, and purchased permission set licenses in the org.

ActiveUserCount.description: Number of users assigned this permission set license who have logged in within the last 30 days.

AssignedUserCount.description: Number of users assigned this permission set license.

DeveloperName.description: The unique name of this permission set license object in the API. This name can contain only underscores and alphanumeric characters, and must be unique in your org. It must begin with a letter, not include spaces, not end with an underscore, and not contain two consecutive underscores.

MasterLabel.description: The label of the permission set license.

MetricsDate.description: Date that permission set license metrics were collected.

PermissionSetLicenseId.description: The ID of the permission set license.

TotalLicenses.description: The total number of this permission set licenses that are available to your org.
